          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Two different sets of U-238 targets were used. The",
                "first one was deposited on a 12.6 um Be backing and",
                "consisted of three arc-shaped (U-238)3(O)8 targets of",
                "1.8 mg/cm2, 1.5 mg/cm2 and 1.6 mg/cm2.",
                "The second target set was deposited on a 8.2 um-thick",
                "Be backing and consisted of three targets comprising",
                "1.0 mg/cm2 of metallic U-238 each, which had been",
                "deposited by sputtering."
              ]
            }
          ],
